x + 8 &> 10, \\
x + 10 &> 8, \\
8 + 10 &> x,
\end{align*} which tell us that $x > 2$, $x > -2$, and $x < 18$.

By the triangle inequality on triangle $CDA$, \begin{align*}
x + 12 &> 16, \\
x + 16 &> 12, \\
12 + 16 &> x,
\end{align*} which tell us that $x > 4$, $x > -4$, and $x < 28$.

